{"title":"13【博客】GitHubPages+Hexo搭建个人博客的相关资料","slug":"13【博客】GitHubPages-Hexo搭建个人博客的资料","date":"2018-10-08T09:11:24.000Z","updated":"2018-10-27T14:16:02.554Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/13【博客】GitHubPages-Hexo搭建个人博客的资料.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"前言Github pages + Hexo + theme yelee折腾折腾～感谢Tim学长和网友wardseptember的帮助Tim的博客wardseptember的博客","covers":["https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006wR0dcly1fw0zt02zpbj314g0m043y.jpg","https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006wR0dcly1fw0zv3qy0uj311a0omq6v.jpg"],"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"/assets/css/APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h2><blockquote>\n<p>Github pages + Hexo + theme yelee</p>\n<p>折腾折腾～</p>\n<p>感谢Tim学长和网友wardseptember的帮助</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zouchanglin.github.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tim的博客</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wardseptember.me\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">wardseptember的博客</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"1-搭建博客\"><a href=\"#1-搭建博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1 搭建博客\"></a>1 搭建博客</h3><blockquote>\n<p>我使用的主题：<a href=\"http://moxfive.xyz/yelee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://moxfive.xyz/yelee/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://zouchanglin.github.io/2018/05/08/2018050801/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tim的博客:Github+hexo+next主题博客搭建教程</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/863f3f2d1733\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">使用github+Hexo人人都能拥有一个美美的博客</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/fengxiongZz/p/7707219.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">使用Hexo+Github一步步搭建属于自己的博客</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-一些美化设置以及我踩的坑\"><a href=\"#2-一些美化设置以及我踩的坑\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2 一些美化设置以及我踩的坑\"></a>2 一些美化设置以及我踩的坑</h3><ul>\n<li>评论</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>有几个是需要科学上网才能加的～</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.janszeng.top/2017/08/31/hexo_yilia_uyan_changyan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">添加友言畅言评论支持</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/lynnbest/article/details/79845944\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo yilia 主题一揽子使用方案</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>优化</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>百度爬虫爬不到GitHub Pages上的内容～</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://ziven.cc/2018/06/28/Yilia%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Yilia主题优化:动态标签和鼠标❤️形效果</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yq.aliyun.com/articles/8608\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo折腾记——性能优化篇</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/sunshine940326/article/details/70936988/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo高阶教程：SEO优化</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>相册</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>1.python脚本里的文件路径要写对</p>\n<p>2.ins.js里的图片存储路径也要正确</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006wR0dcly1fw0zt02zpbj314g0m043y.jpg\" alt=\"INS.JS\"></p>\n<p>3.ins.js调用data.js的路径(我就是因为这个路径没写对，一天多的时间，都在弄这个，最后看到了这句)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006wR0dcly1fw0zv3qy0uj311a0omq6v.jpg\" alt=\"ins.js\"></p>\n<p>4.python版本要对(我电脑里有py2.7和py3.5两个版本，在用pip安装包的时候要下载对应的版本)</p>\n<p>5.我图片存在七牛上了，这样加载快一些。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/a9f309aaa0e0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo Yilia 主题如何添加相册功能</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u013082989/article/details/70162293\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo+Github实现相册功能</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/wardseptember/article/details/82780684\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo+yilia完美实现相册功能（解决缩略图不显示）</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>宠物</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这里我遇到的问题是npm源的问题。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/c59a15d90759\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo 给自己的博客添加萌宠或萌妹子</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_22656383/article/details/79393146\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo 博客小功能添加-评论、萌妹纸、相册、字数统计</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>音乐/视频</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u013082989/article/details/70212008\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo+yilia主题实现文章目录和添加视频</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://tc9011.com/2016/12/24/hexo%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E3%80%81high%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%9D%91/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo添加音乐、high一下及一些坑</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/26a7fc7cc185\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo博客中插入音乐/视频/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.lookk.cn/2017/12/09/heox-%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">heox 添加音乐</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/666274833/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">如何获取音乐外链</a></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"博客","slug":"博客","count":1,"path":"api/tags/博客.json"}]}